data.title: HR Heads All India 16170
data.meta_description: HR Heads All India 16170 - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document contains a list of company names and the names and designations of their respective HR Heads. There are over 200 entries listing an Indian company name followed by the name of its HR Head and their position as "HR Head". The list appears to be providing contact information for HR leaders of various companies in India.
